<pb ed="T" id="T14.0514.0785c" n="0785c"/>
<lb n="0785c01"/>
<milestone unit="juan" n="1"/>
<lb n="0785c02"/><head type="no">No. 514 [Nos. 515, 516]</head>
<lb n="0785c03"/><juan fun="open" n="001"><mulu type="卷" n="001"/><jhead>佛說諫王<note n="0785018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">經＋（一卷）【聖】</note><app n="0785018"><lem>經</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">經一卷</rdg></app></jhead></juan>
<lb n="0785c04"/>
<lb n="0785c05"/><byline type="Translator"><note n="0785019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">宋安陽侯＝宋居士【宋】【宮】，劉宋居士【元】【明】，〔宋安…譯〕－【聖】</note><note n="0785019" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔宋安陽侯沮渠京聲譯〕－【聖】，宋安陽侯＝宋居士【宋】【宮】，宋安陽侯＝劉宋居士【元】【明】</note><app n="0785019"><lem>宋安陽侯沮渠京聲譯</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">宋居士沮渠京聲譯</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">劉宋居士沮渠京聲譯</rdg></app></byline>
<lb n="0785c06"/><div1 type="jing"><p><note n="0785020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">如是我聞＝聞如是【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785020" resp="CBETA" type="mod">如是我聞＝聞如是【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785020"><lem>如是我聞</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">聞如是</rdg></app>。一時佛在舍衛國祇樹給孤獨園。
<lb n="0785c07"/><note n="0785021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔是時國〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785021" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔是時國〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785021"><lem>是時國</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>王名不離先尼。出行國界道過佛所。
<lb n="0785c08"/>身蒙塵土解劍退<note n="0785022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蓋＝坐【聖】</note><app n="0785022"><lem>蓋</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">坐</rdg></app>為佛作禮。<note n="0785023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">天＝世【明】</note><app n="0785023"><lem>天</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">世</rdg></app>尊曰。就
<lb n="0785c09"/>坐。王即坐。佛問王。王所從來身蒙塵土。王即
<lb n="0785c10"/>退坐稽首對諾。屬行國界有災異者。佛告王
<lb n="0785c11"/><note n="0785024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔曰〕－【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0785024"><lem>曰</lem><rdg wit="【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。王治當以<note n="0785025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">正＝政【三】【宮】＊</note><note n="0785025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">正＝政【宋】【元】【明】【宮】＊</note><app n="0785025"><lem>正</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">政</rdg></app>法無失節度。常以慈心養
<lb n="0785c12"/>育人民。所以得霸治為<note n="0785026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔國〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785026"><lem>國</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>王者。皆由宿命
<lb n="0785c13"/>行善所致。統理民事不可偏枉。諸公卿群<note n="0785027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">寮＝僚【聖】＊</note><app n="0785027"><lem>寮</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">僚</rdg></app>
<lb n="0785c14"/>下逮凡民皆有怨辭。<note n="0785028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔王治〕－【三】【宮】，〔王〕－【聖】</note><note n="0785028" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔王治〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，〔王〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785028"><lem>王治</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">治</rdg></app><note n="0785029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">行＝正【聖】</note><app n="0785029"><lem>行</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">正</rdg></app>不<note n="0785030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">平＋（等）【三】【宮】</note><note n="0785030" resp="CBETA" type="mod">平＋（等）【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0785030"><lem>平</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">平等</rdg></app>海內皆
<lb n="0785c15"/>忿。身死<note n="0785031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔魂〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785031"><lem>魂</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>神<note n="0785032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝當【三】【宮】，〔常〕－【聖】</note><note n="0785032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝當【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，〔常〕－【聖】</note><app n="0785032"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">當</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>入太山地獄。後雖悔之無
<lb n="0785c16"/>所復及。王治國平<app type="＊" source="0785025"><lem>正</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】">政</rdg></app>常以節度。臣民歎德
<lb n="0785c17"/>四海歸心。天龍鬼神皆聞王善死得上天後
<lb n="0785c18"/>亦無悔。王無好<note n="0785033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬&CB00105;＝婬泆【元】，淫泆【明】</note><note n="0785033" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬&CB00105;＝婬泆【元】，＝淫泆【明】</note><app n="0785033"><lem>婬&CB00105;</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">婬泆</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">淫泆</rdg></app>以自荒<note n="0785034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">壞＝懷【聖】</note><app n="0785034"><lem>壞</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">懷</rdg></app>。無以忿意
<lb n="0785c19"/>有所殘賊。當受忠臣剛直之諫。夫與人言。常
<lb n="0785c20"/>以寬詳無灼熱之。當以四意待於國民。何謂
<lb n="0785c21"/>為四。隨時廩與。和意與語。所有珍寶與民
<lb n="0785c22"/>共之。<note n="0785035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">占＝瞻【聖】</note><app n="0785035"><lem>占</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">瞻</rdg></app>視老病及諸<note n="0785036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">鰥＝孤【聖】</note><app n="0785036"><lem>鰥</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">孤</rdg></app>寡。王如是者。國中
<lb n="0785c23"/>和平即得其福壽終上天所願自然。王不可
<lb n="0785c24"/>以常得自在。人皆敬畏以之為樂。名象好馬
<lb n="0785c25"/>寶車賢臣。群<app type="＊" source="0785027"><lem>寮</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">僚</rdg></app>百官導從前後。內藏珍寶
<lb n="0785c26"/>倉<note n="0785037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">庫＝穀【聖】</note><app n="0785037"><lem>庫</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">穀</rdg></app>百物。皆當腐壞無長存者。年少會老
<lb n="0785c27"/>強健必病。含血之類皆當歸死。珍寶妻子<note n="0785038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">家室＝室家【聖】</note><app n="0785038"><lem>家
<lb n="0785c28"/>室</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">室家</rdg></app>內外不可<note n="0785039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常得＝得常【聖】</note><app n="0785039"><lem>常得</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">得常</rdg></app>。如人夢見殿舍好園樹木
<lb n="0785c29"/><note n="0785040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">花果＝生&CB00031;【宋】【元】【宮】，生果【明】，生葉【聖】</note><note n="0785040" resp="CBETA" type="mod">花果＝生&CB00031;【宋】【元】【宮】，＝生果【明】，＝生葉【聖】</note><app n="0785040"><lem>花果</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho">生&CB00031;</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">生果</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">生葉</rdg></app>池水流泉。遊戲其中快樂無極。寤則
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0514.0786a" n="0786a"/>
<lb n="0786a01"/>霍然莫知所在。&CB00418;世所有皆如人夢。王寧見
<lb n="0786a02"/>樹有華果。華果不能常著樹。青青之葉會有
<lb n="0786a03"/>萎落。天冠巾幘黼<note n="0786001" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">黻＝&unrec;【聖】</note><app n="0786001"><lem>黻</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&unrec;</rdg></app>名服不能常好。流水不
<lb n="0786a04"/>能常滿。放火曠野火盛焰赫不久則滅。暴風
<lb n="0786a05"/>疾雨雷電霹靂。斯<note n="0786002" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">臾＝須【聖】</note><app n="0786002"><lem>臾</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">須</rdg></app>之間霍然不<note n="0786003" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見＝現【聖】</note><app n="0786003"><lem>見</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">現</rdg></app>。日欲
<lb n="0786a06"/>出時星無精光。日之盛明照於天下不久<note n="0786004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">則＝復【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786004" resp="CBETA" type="mod">則＝復【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786004"><lem>則</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">復</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786a07"/>冥。世間無常亦復如是。喻如四面有大石山。
<lb n="0786a08"/>上下皆有六山俱<note n="0786005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">到＝至【聖】</note><app n="0786005"><lem>到</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">至</rdg></app>同時共合。其中人物含
<lb n="0786a09"/>血之類。無有豪賤皆當<note n="0786006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">糜＝磨【聖】</note><app n="0786006"><lem>糜</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">磨</rdg></app>碎。人有四事不
<lb n="0786a10"/>可得止。老至體枯。病來心惱。身死神去。所
<lb n="0786a11"/>有珍寶皆當棄捐不可得保。此四一至不可
<lb n="0786a12"/>得離無避逃處。非口所能守請陳謝。不可<note n="0786007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">財＝以餞【聖】</note><app n="0786007"><lem>財</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">以餞</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786a13"/>許求哀得解。是時所有名象良馬珍寶壯士
<lb n="0786a14"/>群臣百官護導前後。孰能為王排&CB00230;之者。王
<lb n="0786a15"/>寧見師子獸中最猛。遙見群鹿意欲所取便
<lb n="0786a16"/>前搏撮裂食其肉如斯之痛安可言乎。<note n="0786008" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">命＝喻【聖】</note><app n="0786008"><lem>命</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">喻</rdg></app>如
<lb n="0786a17"/>師子取群鹿時。人命欲終身體不寧。血脈為
<lb n="0786a18"/>消面色為變。命日欲促五<note n="0786009" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">藏＝臟【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786009" resp="CBETA" type="mod">藏＝臟【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786009"><lem>藏</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">臟</rdg></app>不治不思飲食。
<lb n="0786a19"/>雖有神&CB00057;良醫善藥不能使愈。口為妄語其
<lb n="0786a20"/>所索者家室恣之。身體皆痛如被掠治。手足
<lb n="0786a21"/><note n="0786010" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00240;＝狂【宋】【宮】，恇【元】【明】</note><note n="0786010" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00240;＝狂【宋】【宮】，＝恇【元】【明】</note><app n="0786010"><lem>&CB00240;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【宮】" resp="Taisho">狂</rdg><rdg wit="【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">恇</rdg></app>攘骨節欲解。口乾息極羸瘦困劣。不能起
<lb n="0786a22"/>居坐臥須人。若得良藥糜粥甘食人當含之。
<lb n="0786a23"/><note n="0786011" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">必＝心【聖】</note><app n="0786011"><lem>必</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">心</rdg></app>復苦極筋脈欲<note n="0786012" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">絕＝斷【聖】</note><app n="0786012"><lem>絕</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">斷</rdg></app>。但有出氣無復報入。
<lb n="0786a24"/>脣燥乾焦。正氣竭盡邪氣在處。舌稍&CB00230;縮面
<lb n="0786a25"/>目無色。耳鼻閉塞不聞聲香。手足拘攣筋急
<lb n="0786a26"/>口噤欲言不能。手或把空<note n="0786013" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">莫索＝摸&CB01857;【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786013" resp="CBETA" type="mod">莫索＝摸&CB01857;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786013"><lem>莫索</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">摸&CB01857;</rdg></app>邊傍。<note n="0786014" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">白＝自【元】，身【明】</note><note n="0786014" resp="CBETA" type="mod">白＝自【元】，＝身【明】</note><app n="0786014"><lem>白</lem><rdg wit="【元】" resp="Taisho">自</rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">身</rdg></app>汗
<lb n="0786a27"/>目淚流出相<note n="0786015" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">續＝屬【聖】</note><app n="0786015"><lem>續</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">屬</rdg></app>。心意著痛識轉消滅無所復
<lb n="0786a28"/>知。<note n="0786016" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">熅＝溫【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786016" resp="CBETA" type="mod">熅＝溫【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786016"><lem>熅</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">溫</rdg></app>去身冷魂神去矣。所有珍寶父母兄弟
<lb n="0786a29"/>妻子。內外知識奴婢皆當棄捐。隨行獨去不
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0514.0786b" n="0786b"/>
<lb n="0786b01"/><note n="0786017" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">知所到＝得自在【聖】</note><app n="0786017"><lem>知所到</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">得自在</rdg></app>。世間雖樂不得久留。王當是時當何
<lb n="0786b02"/>恃怙。唯有孝<note n="0786018" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">順慈養＝慈育養【聖】</note><app n="0786018"><lem>順慈養</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">慈育養</rdg></app>二親。供事高行清潔沙
<lb n="0786b03"/>門<note n="0786019" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">見凡＝凡見【聖】</note><app n="0786019"><lem>見凡</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">凡見</rdg></app>老人當尊敬之。所有財寶與民同
<lb n="0786b04"/>歡。當以<note n="0786020" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">慈＝善【聖】</note><app n="0786020"><lem>慈</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">善</rdg></app>心施惠於民。無以讒言殘<note n="0786021" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">害民＝賊人【聖】</note><app n="0786021"><lem>害民</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">賊人</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786b05"/>命。為王之法當宣聖道。教民為善。<note n="0786022" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">唯＝惟【聖】</note><app n="0786022"><lem>唯</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">惟</rdg></app>守一
<lb n="0786b06"/>心心存三尊。王者如斯諸聖諮嗟。天龍鬼神
<lb n="0786b07"/>擁護其國。生有榮譽死得上天。身死神去當
<lb n="0786b08"/>何所恃。<note n="0786023" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【元】【明】【聖】</note><app n="0786023"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【元】【明】【聖】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>恃善耳。火盛煒<note n="0786024" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">煒＝燁【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786024" resp="CBETA" type="mod">煒＝燁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786024"><lem>煒</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">燁</rdg></app>恃水滅之。飢
<lb n="0786b09"/>渴之人<note n="0786025" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786025" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786025"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app>恃水穀。老恃机杖。盲恃有目。冥
<lb n="0786b10"/>恃燈火。疾病困篤恃良醫藥。船行巨海風浪
<lb n="0786b11"/><note n="0786026" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盛猛＝猛盛【聖】</note><app n="0786026"><lem>盛猛</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">猛盛</rdg></app>恃彼<note n="0786027" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">榜櫓＝傍岸【聖】</note><app n="0786027"><lem>榜櫓</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">傍岸</rdg></app>。道有<note n="0786028" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">盜賊＝賊盜【聖】</note><app n="0786028"><lem>盜賊</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">賊盜</rdg></app>恃藏匿處。身死
<lb n="0786b12"/>神去<note n="0786029" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">惟＝唯【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786029" resp="CBETA" type="mod">惟＝唯【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786029"><lem>惟</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">唯</rdg></app><note n="0786030" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">恃修＝脩恃【聖】</note><app n="0786030"><lem>恃修</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">脩恃</rdg></app>善。<note n="0786031" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">猶＝由【聖】</note><app n="0786031"><lem>猶</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">由</rdg></app>逢彼難各恃其事。以
<lb n="0786b13"/>自拔濟宗室獲安。王無以為樂飲食極味。遊
<lb n="0786b14"/>居自在<note n="0786032" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔不可〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786032" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔不可〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786032"><lem>不可</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>常<note n="0786033" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝恃【聖】</note><app n="0786033"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">恃</rdg></app>。飽滿皆當消散不可常
<lb n="0786b15"/>得。好香塗身苾芬<note n="0786034" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">括＝聒【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786034" resp="CBETA" type="mod">括＝聒【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786034"><lem>括</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">聒</rdg></app>鼻。珠璣瓔珞奕奕<note n="0786035" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">曜＝耀【聖】</note><app n="0786035"><lem>曜</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">耀</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786b16"/>目。水陸好華<note n="0786036" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">以為＝為以【聖】</note><app n="0786036"><lem>以為</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">為以</rdg></app><note n="0786037" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">校＝博【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786037"><lem>校</lem><rdg wit="【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">博</rdg></app>飾。金縷織成以為名
<lb n="0786b17"/>服。白毳衣。文繡衣。雜綵衣。無極衣。細疊衣。
<lb n="0786b18"/>細緻衣。<note n="0786038" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">錦＝繡【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786038"><lem>錦</lem><rdg wit="【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">繡</rdg></app>綾衣。此皆無常不可久保。宮觀
<lb n="0786b19"/>高臺華闕殿舍。黃金白銀七寶床&CB00186;。氍<note n="0786039" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">毹＝氀【聖】</note><app n="0786039"><lem>毹</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">氀</rdg></app>&CB00847;
<lb n="0786b20"/>&CB00846;綩綖細軟以藉身體。<note n="0786040" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">七寶＝金縷【聖】</note><app n="0786040"><lem>七寶</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">金縷</rdg></app>織成文繡綾綺
<lb n="0786b21"/>以為幃帳。柱梁<note n="0786041" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">殿＝壁【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786041" resp="CBETA" type="mod">殿＝壁【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786041"><lem>殿</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">壁</rdg></app>戶彫文刻鏤。燒眾雜香遊
<lb n="0786b22"/>戲其中。斯皆無常不可久保。琴瑟箏笛眾<note n="0786042" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">音＝樂【聖】</note><app n="0786042"><lem>音</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">樂</rdg></app>
<lb n="0786b23"/>集聚。歌舞倡伎眾音盈耳快樂<note n="0786043" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">（不）＋可【聖】</note><app n="0786043"><lem>可</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">不可</rdg></app>言。斯亦無
<lb n="0786b24"/>常如<note n="0786044" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">幻如夢＝夢幻【聖】</note><app n="0786044"><lem>幻如夢</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">夢幻</rdg></app>不<note n="0786045" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">得＝可【聖】</note><app n="0786045"><lem>得</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">可</rdg></app>久保。象馬寶車光目之
<lb n="0786b25"/>觀。王一出時<note n="0786046" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">椎＝推【聖】＊</note><app n="0786046"><lem>椎</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">推</rdg></app>鐘鳴鼓<note n="0786047" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驛＝護【聖】</note><app n="0786047"><lem>驛</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">護</rdg></app>導前後。王乘羽
<lb n="0786b26"/>蓋之車侍者持幢。翠毛<note n="0786048" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB02882;＝葆【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786048" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB02882;＝葆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786048"><lem>&CB02882;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">葆</rdg></app>羽彫文其柄以拂
<lb n="0786b27"/>塵土。治填道路丹畫欄楯。眾民所觀無不敬
<lb n="0786b28"/>畏。好華名香皆以迎王。稱壽萬歲斯亦難保。
<lb n="0786b29"/>王寧見人欲死<note n="0786049" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">時不＝之時【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786049" resp="CBETA" type="mod">時不＝之時【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786049"><lem>時不</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">之時</rdg></app>。諸家內外聚會其邊。
<pb ed="T" id="T14.0514.0786c" n="0786c"/>
<lb n="0786c01"/><app type="＊" source="0786046"><lem>椎</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【聖】">推</rdg></app>胸呼天皆云奈何。<note n="0786050" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB01019;＝&CB01018;【聖】</note><app n="0786050"><lem>&CB01019;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&CB01018;</rdg></app><note n="0786051" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00051;＝咿【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786051" resp="CBETA" type="mod">&CB00051;＝咿【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786051"><lem>&CB00051;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">咿</rdg></app>哽<note n="0786052" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">咽＝噎【聖】</note><app n="0786052"><lem>咽</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">噎</rdg></app>淚下交
<lb n="0786c02"/><note n="0786053" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">流＝橫【聖】</note><app n="0786053"><lem>流</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">橫</rdg></app>。嗚呼痛哉神靈獨逝。<note n="0786054" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔捨〕－【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786054" resp="CBETA" type="mod">〔捨〕－【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786054"><lem>捨</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>吾如之<note n="0786055" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">〔乎〕－【聖】</note><app n="0786055"><lem>乎</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">&lac;</rdg></app>。聞
<lb n="0786c03"/>之者莫不傷心。<note n="0786056" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00418;＝視【聖】</note><app n="0786056"><lem>&CB00418;</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">視</rdg></app>之者莫不助哀。載之出城
<lb n="0786c04"/>捐於曠野。飛鳥走獸<note n="0786057" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">摑&CB02622;＝&CB13437;&CB02622;【三】【宮】，掣抴【聖】</note><note n="0786057" resp="CBETA" type="mod">摑&CB02622;＝&CB13437;&CB02622;【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝掣抴【聖】</note><app n="0786057"><lem>摑&CB02622;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">&CB13437;&CB02622;</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">掣抴</rdg></app>食之。身中有蟲
<lb n="0786c05"/>還食其肉。日炙風飄骨皆為乾。往昔諸王尊
<lb n="0786c06"/>榮豪貴。隱隱闐闐亦如大王。今日霍然不復
<lb n="0786c07"/>見之。此<note n="0786058" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">皆＝者【聖】</note><app n="0786058"><lem>皆</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">者</rdg></app>無常之明<note n="0786059" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">驗＝證【聖】</note><app n="0786059"><lem>驗</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">證</rdg></app>也。古<note n="0786060" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">常＝尚【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786060" resp="CBETA" type="mod">常＝尚【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786060"><lem>常</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">尚</rdg></app>如此況於
<lb n="0786c08"/>今日。王熟思之無念<note n="0786061" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">婬&CB00105;＝婬泆【三】【宮】</note><note n="0786061" resp="CBETA" type="mod">婬&CB00105;＝婬泆【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0786061"><lem>婬&CB00105;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">婬泆</rdg></app>。無受&CB00126;言<note n="0786062" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">證人入＝誤入人【三】【宮】，證入人【聖】</note><note n="0786062" resp="CBETA" type="mod">證人入＝誤入人【宋】【元】【明】【宮】，＝證入人【聖】</note><app n="0786062"><lem>證人
<lb n="0786c09"/>入</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">誤入人</rdg><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">證入人</rdg></app>罪。當受忠諫治以節度。當畏地獄酷治之
<lb n="0786c10"/>痛。諸含血之<note n="0786063" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">蟲＝類【三】【宮】【聖】</note><note n="0786063" resp="CBETA" type="mod">蟲＝類【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】</note><app n="0786063"><lem>蟲</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】【聖】" resp="Taisho">類</rdg></app>皆貪生活不當殺之。佛說經
<lb n="0786c11"/>竟。王意即解願為弟子即受五戒。頭面著地
<lb n="0786c12"/>為佛作<note n="0786064" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">禮＋（而去）【聖】</note><app n="0786064"><lem>禮</lem><rdg wit="【聖】" resp="Taisho">禮而去</rdg></app><note n="0786065" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">光明皇后願文【聖】</note></p>
<lb n="0786c13"/><trailer>佛說諫王經</trailer><juan fun="close" n="001"></juan></div1>
</body></text></TEI.2>